Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:03.33,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:07.09,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:11.05,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.55,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.93,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.06,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.40,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:35.61,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:38.74,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:47.63,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.80,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.59,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.72,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.18,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.27,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.81,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}会有梦想绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.52,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不管何时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.78,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}伴随左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:16.28,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}我们一起
